%N A394179 Least Carmichael number (A002997) that is the product of exactly n primes congruent to 3 modulo 4.
%C A394179 If k is an odd number with at least 3 distinct prime factors, then the number of bases in (Z/kZ)^* in which k is a strong pseudoprime at most phi(k)/2^(omega(k)-1), where equality holds if and only if k is a Carmichael number with only prime factors congruent to 3 modulo 4 (A329468). See A329759 for a proof.
